<item>
            <title>[JCR-2128] Adding DerbyDataStore to handle proper close of the embedded database</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-2128</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>When using embedded Derby in conjunction with DbDataStore, the Derby database is never shutdown, as it requires special code to be executed (creating a Connection with &amp;quot;;shutdown=true&amp;quot;)&lt;br/&gt;
We may provide a DerbyDataStore extending standard DbDataStore for handling that.</description>
